description: With summer vacation over, Catarina and the others are gearing up for a practical exam. The condition to pass is to retrieve a stone inhabited by magical power from the depths of some ancient ruins. Catarina teams up with Geordo, Keith, and Sophia to enter this complex dungeon filled with traps.

titles.title: Kiken na Dungeon ni Haitte Shimatta...
Zut, je suis entrée dans un donjon périlleux…
危険なダンジョンに入ってしまった...
